{"tid":616912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身為女人係香港一定要好好保護自己","createTime":"2018-04-04T14:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T18:18:27.000Z","uid":6783,"like":67,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca2abb31ac3520c19820e48ac5a9bbc4f58d677","tid":616912,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"我今日就食雲呑麵 <br />\n點知搭枱嗰個阿叔話我對筷子揸得唔啱<br />\n仲隊佢嗰對筷子去我臉前話教我<br />\n仲不停咁嘆氣話 唉  依家啲後生連筷子都揸唔啱<br />\n一開始都算 我忍佢<br />\n點知越食佢就越講 仲望住我喺度唉唉聲<br />\n我就話 你再係咁我就唔客氣<br />\n跟住佢就話 唏 你d後生女做到d咩<br />\n咁我梗係好嬲啦 細細聲同佢講 你玩完了<br />\n之後我就大嗌 非禮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個阿叔非禮我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢即刻比店員欄住 有幾個後生仔幫我禁住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教我揸筷子啊拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身敗名裂啦你"},{"pid":"fcd113ae3321bd92ad48d94a1a0a9a7ae826eb93","tid":616912,"uid":43042,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:40:27.000Z","msg":"做得好<br />\n呢D阿叔廢老直頭要拎去打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c81ff8f2303a631ec92ff4ec13dfa6c3c8f7e50","tid":616912,"uid":45148,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:40:44.000Z","msg":"標題應該係<br />\n<br />\n身為廢老係香港一定要好好保護自己"},{"pid":"33bcc2f3c04a5eb686626796863e6ddf3700f4f5","tid":616912,"uid":19255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"Ching好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fefa49156c9085d68b8233d26f71109df5fef64","tid":616912,"uid":175159,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:43:35.000Z","msg":"善用起底功能 176 男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba36b210064ddefc9e43dcf5f3b2ee5c79a577ad","tid":616912,"uid":6783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33bcc2f3c04a5eb686626796863e6ddf3700f4